    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>sweet pointed pepper[s]</strong> into rings</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over the highest heat</p><p>Once your pan is hot, add the <strong>sliced pepper </strong>and cook for 3 min or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1970-v2-Step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
