            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pepper is softening, boil half a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a bowl with your <strong>soured cream</strong> and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>chipotle cream</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
