    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained black beans</strong>, your <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong> and <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>and<strong> </strong>cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> and a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and cook for 3 min or until thickened – these are your <strong>smoky beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
