    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>smoky beans</strong> between the<strong> warmed tortillas </strong>and top with the <strong>shredded</strong> <strong>lettuce </strong>and your <strong>smashed avocado</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the<strong> chipotle cream</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
